attributes.title: F**KFACE OFF Episode 1: Nick VS. Eric
attributes.caption: Hello and welcome to the first of six episodes of F**KFACE OFF!  The premier sporting league in the known observable universe that pits Andrew, Nick, Eric, Geoff, and Gavin's (ANEGG) simulation ready baseball teams against one another to determine who should have a billboard erected in their name in Deputy, Indiana.
attributes.description: Hello and welcome to the first of six episodes of F**KFACE OFF!  The premier sporting league in the known observable universe that pits Andrew, Nick, Eric, Geoff, and Gavin's (ANEGG) simulation ready baseball teams against one another to determine who should have a billboard erected in their name in Deputy, Indiana.  In this episode, Nick and Eric will square off to open the gates on what will be a thrilling season of F**KFACE OFF baseball.
